post_content.caption: Should the EU continue to support Ukraine? Our poll finds Europeans are in favour
post_content.description:
Most of the respondents of an exclusive poll for Euronews by IPSOS say support to Ukraine should continue. But they are in two minds about whether it should be a priority for the next mandate. 

READ MORE : https://www.euronews.com/2024/03/28/should-the-eu-continue-to-support-ukraine-our-poll-finds-europeans-are-in-favour
